{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_08_01_short",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 1話 一週間マネージャー (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――遙子がサニーピースに加わる数年前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few years ago before Haruko joining Sunny Peace",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今日から一週間、遙子さんのマネージャーを\nすることになりました。改めてよろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Starting today for a week‚ I'll be Haruko-san's manager.\nNice to meet you again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.933333385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "君はずっと麻奈ちゃんの担当だったから\n私のマネージャーなんてなんだか変な感じね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've always been with Mana-chan‚\nso having you as my manager feels a bit odd.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.3000000517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。でも、やるからには精一杯務めるので\n俺にしてほしいことがあればなんでも言って下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it does. But I'll do my best since I've taken it on.\nIf there's anything you want me to do‚ just say the word.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.5999996702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "なんでも……？\nじゃあ、さっそくお願いしてもいいかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anything…?\nAlright then‚ can I ask you something right away?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.6666659553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "私が{user}君にしてほしいことは……\n敬語禁止よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What I want from you‚ {user}‚ is…\nBan on honorifics.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.6666654467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "前々から思ってたけど、君の方が年上で\n高校の先輩でもあるのに、どうしていつも敬語なの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been thinking for a while now‚ but why do you always use honorifics\neven though you're older and my senior in high school?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.6666629035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それは……この業界では遙子さんの方が先輩ですから\nそれに遙子さんは年下って気がしなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… In this industry‚ you're the senior‚ Haruko-san.\nAnd it's not like I feel you're younger…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.1999962369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "私の方が年上に見えるってこと？\nピチピチのJKを捕まえてそれは酷いんじゃないかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you think I look older?\nIsn't it harsh to talk to fresh-faced high schooler like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.9333290616,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}